---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="AI & Automation Workshop Package"
  description="A three-tier engagement framework for delivering AI and automation workshops. From half-day discovery to two-day build hackathons."
>
  <div class="container">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="ws-header">
      <p class="ws-site">builtwithjon.com</p>
      <h1>AI &amp; Automation Workshop Package</h1>
      <p class="ws-desc">A three-tier engagement framework for delivering AI and automation workshops. From half-day discovery to two-day build hackathons. Built from 20+ years running these at enterprise scale.</p>
      <span class="ws-badge">INTERNAL &middot; v1.0 &middot; April 2026</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Tier Tabs -->
    <div class="ws-tabs" role="tablist" aria-label="Workshop tiers">
      <button class="ws-tab active" role="tab" id="tab-1" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="panel-1" data-tier="1">Tier 1 &mdash; Discovery</button>
      <button class="ws-tab" role="tab" id="tab-2" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="panel-2" data-tier="2">Tier 2 &mdash; Sprint</button>
      <button class="ws-tab" role="tab" id="tab-3" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="panel-3" data-tier="3">Tier 3 &mdash; Hackathon</button>
    </div>

    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!-- TIER 1 — Discovery Session                                   -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <div class="ws-panel active" id="panel-1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-1" data-panel="1">
      <h2>Discovery Session</h2>

      <div class="ws-meta">
        <div class="ws-meta-item">
          <span class="ws-meta-label">Duration</span>
          <span class="ws-meta-value">Half Day (3-4 hours)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ws-meta-item">
          <span class="ws-meta-label">Ideal For</span>
          <span class="ws-meta-value">Early-stage deals, SMB clients, or scoping larger engagements</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ws-meta-item">
          <span class="ws-meta-label">Price Range</span>
          <span class="ws-meta-value ws-price">$2,500 &ndash; $5,000</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Overview</h3>
      <p>A focused, facilitated session that maps the client's current workflows, identifies automation opportunities, and delivers a prioritized shortlist with rough ROI estimates. The client walks away knowing exactly where to start.</p>

      <h3>Agenda</h3>
      <div class="ws-agenda">
        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">0:00&ndash;0:15</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Kickoff &amp; Objectives</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Align on goals, introduce the framework, set expectations for deliverables.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">0:15&ndash;1:00</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Current State Mapping</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Walk through 3-5 core workflows. Document inputs, outputs, systems, handoffs, pain points. Use the Process Inventory Worksheet.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">1:00&ndash;1:45</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Opportunity Identification</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Brainstorm automation and AI opportunities for each workflow. Capture on the Opportunity Canvas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item ws-agenda-break">
          <span class="ws-agenda-time">1:45&ndash;2:00</span>
          <span class="ws-agenda-title">Break</span>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">2:00&ndash;2:45</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Impact vs. Effort Scoring</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Score each opportunity on business impact (revenue, cost, risk, time) and implementation effort. Plot on the Priority Matrix.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">2:45&ndash;3:15</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Quick Wins &amp; Roadmap</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Identify top 3 quick wins and sequence them into a 30/60/90 day view.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">3:15&ndash;3:30</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Wrap-Up &amp; Next Steps</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Summarize findings, confirm deliverables timeline, discuss engagement options.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Client Deliverables</h3>
      <ol class="ws-deliverables">
        <li>Process Inventory (documented current-state workflows)</li>
        <li>Prioritized Opportunity List with impact/effort scores</li>
        <li>Top 3 Quick Wins with estimated ROI ranges</li>
        <li>30/60/90 Day Roadmap (high level)</li>
        <li>Executive Summary (1-2 pages, delivered within 48 hours)</li>
      </ol>

      <h3>Closing Move</h3>
      <div class="ws-closing">
        <p>The Discovery Session is designed to naturally lead into a Tier 2 Sprint or a scoped implementation engagement. The deliverables create urgency by showing the client exactly how much they're leaving on the table.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!-- TIER 2 — Automation Sprint                                   -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <div class="ws-panel" id="panel-2" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-2" data-panel="2">
      <h2>Automation Sprint</h2>

      <div class="ws-meta">
        <div class="ws-meta-item">
          <span class="ws-meta-label">Duration</span>
          <span class="ws-meta-value">Full Day (6-7 hours)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ws-meta-item">
          <span class="ws-meta-label">Ideal For</span>
          <span class="ws-meta-value">Mid-size deals, clients ready to commit, or teams needing cross-department alignment</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ws-meta-item">
          <span class="ws-meta-label">Price Range</span>
          <span class="ws-meta-value ws-price">$7,500 &ndash; $15,000</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Overview</h3>
      <p>A deeper engagement that goes beyond discovery into solution design. The team maps workflows, scores opportunities, selects the top candidates, and designs the automation architecture for the first 1-2 use cases. Ends with a buildable spec.</p>

      <h3>Agenda</h3>
      <div class="ws-agenda">
        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">0:00&ndash;0:20</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Kickoff &amp; Alignment</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Review pre-work submissions. Align stakeholders on objectives, success criteria, and constraints.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">0:20&ndash;1:30</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Deep Process Mapping</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Map 5-8 workflows in detail. Document systems, data flows, decision points, exceptions, and volumes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">1:30&ndash;2:15</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Opportunity Scoring</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Score all identified opportunities using the weighted Priority Matrix (business value, feasibility, risk, speed to value).</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item ws-agenda-break">
          <span class="ws-agenda-time">2:15&ndash;2:45</span>
          <span class="ws-agenda-title">Lunch Break</span>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">2:45&ndash;3:45</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Use Case Deep Dive</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Select top 2 use cases. Define scope, inputs/outputs, success metrics, integration requirements, and estimated effort.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">3:45&ndash;4:45</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Solution Architecture</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Design the automation/AI architecture for the top use case. Map the tooling (n8n, Make, custom, AI agents), data flow, and integration points.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item ws-agenda-break">
          <span class="ws-agenda-time">4:45&ndash;5:00</span>
          <span class="ws-agenda-title">Break</span>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">5:00&ndash;5:45</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">ROI Modeling</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Build a simple ROI model for the top 2 use cases. Hours saved, error reduction, revenue impact, payback period.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">5:45&ndash;6:15</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Roadmap &amp; Resourcing</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Sequence the implementation. Define phases, milestones, team requirements, and timeline.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">6:15&ndash;6:30</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Executive Readout</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Present findings and recommendations to stakeholders. Confirm next steps.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Client Deliverables</h3>
      <ol class="ws-deliverables">
        <li>Detailed Process Maps for 5-8 workflows</li>
        <li>Scored Priority Matrix with weighted criteria</li>
        <li>Use Case Specs for top 2 opportunities (scope, metrics, architecture)</li>
        <li>Solution Architecture Diagram for primary use case</li>
        <li>ROI Model with payback timeline</li>
        <li>Implementation Roadmap with phases and milestones</li>
        <li>Executive Readout Deck (delivered within 5 business days)</li>
      </ol>

      <h3>Closing Move</h3>
      <div class="ws-closing">
        <p>The Sprint deliverables are designed to be the Statement of Work for the implementation phase. The client has already bought in emotionally during the session &mdash; the readout deck makes the business case for their leadership.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!-- TIER 3 — Build Hackathon                                     -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <div class="ws-panel" id="panel-3" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-3" data-panel="3">
      <h2>Build Hackathon</h2>

      <div class="ws-meta">
        <div class="ws-meta-item">
          <span class="ws-meta-label">Duration</span>
          <span class="ws-meta-value">Two Days</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ws-meta-item">
          <span class="ws-meta-label">Ideal For</span>
          <span class="ws-meta-value">Committed clients, larger deals, or teams that want to see something working first</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ws-meta-item">
          <span class="ws-meta-label">Price Range</span>
          <span class="ws-meta-value ws-price">$15,000 &ndash; $30,000+</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Overview</h3>
      <p>A hands-on, intensive engagement where the team doesn't just plan &mdash; they build. Day 1 covers discovery and design. Day 2 is pure execution: the team prototypes a working automation or AI agent. The client walks away with something running, not just a document.</p>

      <h3>Agenda</h3>
      <div class="ws-agenda">

        <div class="ws-agenda-day">Day 1</div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">0:00&ndash;0:30</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Kickoff &amp; Team Formation</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Set objectives. Form cross-functional teams (client + consultants). Assign roles.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">0:30&ndash;2:00</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Accelerated Discovery</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Rapid process mapping. Focus on the 2-3 highest-impact workflows pre-identified in intake.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">2:00&ndash;3:00</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Use Case Selection &amp; Scoping</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Score, select, and tightly scope the build target. Define what "done" looks like by end of Day 2.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item ws-agenda-break">
          <span class="ws-agenda-time">3:00&ndash;3:15</span>
          <span class="ws-agenda-title">Break</span>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">3:15&ndash;5:00</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Solution Design &amp; Architecture</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Design the full solution. Map integrations, data flows, AI components, and automation logic.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">5:00&ndash;5:30</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Day 1 Wrap &amp; Build Prep</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Confirm the build plan. Assign Day 2 tasks. Set up environments and access.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-day">Day 2</div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">0:00&ndash;0:15</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Day 2 Kickoff</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Review build plan. Confirm access and environments. Go.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">0:15&ndash;12:00</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Build Sprint (Morning)</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Heads-down building. Checkpoint every 90 minutes. Consultants pair with client team members.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item ws-agenda-break">
          <span class="ws-agenda-time">12:00&ndash;12:30</span>
          <span class="ws-agenda-title">Lunch</span>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">12:30&ndash;3:00</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Build Sprint (Afternoon)</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Continue building. Integration testing. Polish the demo flow.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item ws-agenda-break">
          <span class="ws-agenda-time">3:00&ndash;3:30</span>
          <span class="ws-agenda-title">Break &amp; Demo Prep</span>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">3:30&ndash;4:15</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Live Demo &amp; Review</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Demo the working prototype to stakeholders. Walk through what was built, what it does, and what it would take to productionize.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-agenda-item" data-expandable>
          <button class="ws-agenda-header" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ws-agenda-time">4:15&ndash;5:00</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-title">Roadmap &amp; Engagement Planning</span>
            <span class="ws-agenda-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
          </button>
          <div class="ws-agenda-detail">
            <p>Define what production looks like. Scope the next phase. Close.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Client Deliverables</h3>
      <ol class="ws-deliverables">
        <li>Working Prototype (automation, AI agent, or integration &mdash; running in a staging environment)</li>
        <li>Solution Architecture Document</li>
        <li>Build Documentation (what was built, how it works, how to extend it)</li>
        <li>ROI Projection tied to the working prototype</li>
        <li>Production Roadmap with effort estimates</li>
        <li>Executive Summary with demo recording</li>
      </ol>

      <h3>Closing Move</h3>
      <div class="ws-closing">
        <p>Nothing closes a deal like a working demo. The client's team built it alongside you &mdash; they have ownership. The conversation shifts from "should we do this" to "when do we go live." That's the whole point.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!-- Supporting Worksheets                                        -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <div class="ws-worksheets">
      <button class="ws-worksheets-toggle" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="ws-worksheets-content">
        <h2>Supporting Worksheets</h2>
        <span class="ws-worksheets-chevron" aria-hidden="true">&rsaquo;</span>
      </button>
      <div class="ws-worksheets-content" id="ws-worksheets-content">
        <div class="ws-worksheet">
          <div class="ws-worksheet-header">
            <strong>Process Inventory Worksheet</strong>
            <span class="ws-worksheet-tiers">All tiers</span>
          </div>
          <p>Captures current-state workflows: inputs, outputs, systems involved, handoffs, pain points, volume, and frequency.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-worksheet">
          <div class="ws-worksheet-header">
            <strong>Opportunity Canvas</strong>
            <span class="ws-worksheet-tiers">All tiers</span>
          </div>
          <p>One-page capture for each automation opportunity: problem statement, proposed solution, affected roles, estimated impact, and dependencies.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-worksheet">
          <div class="ws-worksheet-header">
            <strong>Priority Matrix / Impact vs. Effort</strong>
            <span class="ws-worksheet-tiers">All tiers</span>
          </div>
          <p>Weighted scoring framework. Configurable criteria: business value, feasibility, risk, speed to value, strategic alignment.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-worksheet">
          <div class="ws-worksheet-header">
            <strong>ROI Model Template</strong>
            <span class="ws-worksheet-tiers">Tier 2 &amp; 3</span>
          </div>
          <p>Simple spreadsheet model: hours saved &times; loaded cost, error reduction value, revenue uplift, implementation cost, payback period.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-worksheet">
          <div class="ws-worksheet-header">
            <strong>Solution Architecture Template</strong>
            <span class="ws-worksheet-tiers">Tier 2 &amp; 3</span>
          </div>
          <p>Visual template for mapping automation/AI architecture: tools, integrations, data flows, decision points, and human-in-the-loop touchpoints.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Page Footer -->
    <div class="ws-page-footer">
      <span>builtwithjon.com</span>
      <span class="ws-confidential">NOT FOR CLIENT DISTRIBUTION</span>
    </div>

  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  /* Workshop page — header */
  .ws-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .ws-site {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .ws-header h1 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .ws-desc {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .ws-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    background: var(--color-code-bg);
    padding: 0.2em 0.6em;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  /* Tabs */
  .ws-tabs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-border);
